title: This is why duo queue should be removed
body:
http://imgur.com/4FZhbaV

Shit like this happens.

* About 5 minutes into the game
* Zed goes for my wolves
* I take them. My jungle
* Zed decides to feed
* Grag defends Zed's actions for about 15 minutes
* I'm like 1/5
* Grag is dominating his lane, Thresh and Ez are dominating too
* I make a massive comeback and start getting doubles left and right
* Enemy TF says, "COMEBACK SEASON"
* Grag decides that he doesn't want that to happen
* Grag starts to feed too
* We end up losing when we were so close to winning
* Thanks duo queue
